(iv) 

Reporting. 

Each owner or operator of a facility which is subject to the limitations of paragraphs (b)(3)(iii)(B) 

(1)

 through 

(5)

 of this section, as described under paragraph (b)(3)(ii) of this section shall submit to the Administrator by March
1 of each calendar year, beginning in 2002, a certification of compliance with this section for the previous calendar
year. This certification shall include: 

(A) A declaration that the facility is in compliance with all of the requirements of this section; and 



